    {
      "type": "text", "id": "traffic-content", "x": 70, "y": 560, "width": 480, "height": 380,
      "text": "Facebook/Instagram Ads ($100-250/day)\n  2 ad sets x 5 creatives\n  Target: clinic owners, dentists,\n    med spa owners, chiropractors\n  Geo: US (FL, TX, CA, NY)\n  Age: 28-55\n\nInstagram Reels + Stories (3-5/week)\nSkool Community Posts (weekly)\nEmail Blast (Tuesday before)\nSMS Blast (Tuesday + Thursday AM)\n\nRetargeting: website visitors\nLookalike: existing leads + buyers\n\nAd Types:\n  Pattern interrupt hook\n  Case study lead\n  Curiosity gap\n  Direct registration\n  UGC / Testimonial",
      "fontSize": 16, "fontFamily": 1, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null, "originalText": "Facebook/Instagram Ads ($100-250/day)\n  2 ad sets x 5 creatives\n  Target: clinic owners, dentists,\n    med spa owners, chiropractors\n  Geo: US (FL, TX, CA, NY)\n  Age: 28-55\n\nInstagram Reels + Stories (3-5/week)\nSkool Community Posts (weekly)\nEmail Blast (Tuesday before)\nSMS Blast (Tuesday + Thursday AM)\n\nRetargeting: website visitors\nLookalike: existing leads + buyers\n\nAd Types:\n  Pattern interrupt hook\n  Case study lead\n  Curiosity gap\n  Direct registration\n  UGC / Testimonial",
