    {
      "type": "text", "id": "nurture-content", "x": 620, "y": 1060, "width": 540, "height": 320,
      "text": "IMMEDIATELY: SMS + Email confirmation\n\nWED 10AM: Day-before reminder\n  SMS + Email with social proof\n\nTHU 9AM: \"Today's the day!\" (SMS)\nTHU 6PM: \"60 minutes!\" + join link (SMS)\nTHU 6:30PM: Join link + checklist (Email)\nTHU 7PM: \"We're LIVE!\" (SMS)\nTHU 7:05PM: No-show nudge (SMS)\n\nGHL Workflow: \"Webinar Pre-Show Nurture\"\nTrigger: Tag 'webinar-registered'\nExit: Webinar starts\n\nTarget: 45%+ show-up rate",
